kgr:sky a kg:Company ; skos:prefLabel "Sky (Comcast)" ; rdfs:comment "Major UK broadband and TV competitor" ; kg:industry kgr:ind_telecom ; kg:incorporated_in kgr:jurisdiction_uk .
